@startuml
```plantuml
@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome

' ============================================
' 第一步：涉众 → Actor 映射
' ============================================
actor "库房人员" as WarehouseStaff
actor "运维工程师" as MaintenanceEngineer
actor "招商业务员" as SalesRep
actor "财务人员" as FinanceStaff
actor "库房主管" as WarehouseManager
actor "运维负责人" as MaintenanceManager
actor "总监" as Director

' ============================================
' 第二步：用例提取与合并/拆分
' ============================================
rectangle "设备管理" {
  ' 合并 BR-EQP-001, BR-EQP-002, BR-EQP-009, BR-EQP-011 → 出库校验与特批
  usecase "UC1: 执行设备出库校验" as UC1
  usecase "UC2: 发起紧急出库特批" as UC2
  usecase "UC3: 审批紧急出库特批" as UC3
  
  ' 合并 BR-EQP-003, BR-EQP-004, BR-EQP-007, BR-EQP-008, BR-EQP-010, BR-EQP-012 → 归还验收
  usecase "UC4: 执行设备归还验收" as UC4
  
  ' 合并 BR-EQP-005, BR-EQP-006, BR-EQP-014, BR-EQP-015 → 校准管理
  usecase "UC5: 管理校准预警配置" as UC5
  usecase "UC6: 接收校准提醒" as UC6
  
  ' BR-EQP-013 → 押金复核
  usecase "UC7: 复核押金退还" as UC7
}

rectangle "租赁订单" {
  ' 合并 BR-ORD-001, BR-ORD-003, BR-ORD-005 → 合同变更
  usecase "UC8: 发起合同变更" as UC8
  
  ' BR-ORD-002 → 流程固化
  usecase "UC9: 执行标准租赁流程" as UC9
  
  ' BR-ORD-004 → 信息同步
  usecase "UC10: 同步签约信息" as UC10
  
  ' BR-ORD-006 → 紧急判断
  usecase "UC11: 判断紧急出库等级" as UC11
}

' ============================================
' 第三步：建立关系
' ============================================

' Actor 与用例关联
WarehouseStaff --> UC1
WarehouseStaff --> UC4
WarehouseStaff --> UC6

MaintenanceEngineer --> UC2
MaintenanceEngineer --> UC4

SalesRep --> UC8
SalesRep --> UC9

FinanceStaff --> UC7

WarehouseManager --> UC3
MaintenanceManager --> UC3
Director --> UC3

' <<include>> 关系
UC1 .> UC11 : <<include>>
UC9 .> UC10 : <<include>>

' <<extend>> 关系
UC8 ..> UC2 : <<extend>>
UC4 ..> UC7 : <<extend>>

' ============================================
' 第四步：附加注解
' ============================================
note right of WarehouseStaff
  **Actor映射决策**
  库房人员→库房人员：直接操作出库/入库
  运维工程师→运维工程师：技术判定角色
  招商业务员→招商业务员：合同管理角色
  财务人员→财务人员：资金安全角色
  库房主管/运维负责人/总监→审批角色
end note

note right of UC1
  **用例合并理由**
  BR-EQP-001（自动校验）和BR-EQP-002（特批通道）
  是同一业务流程的两个分支，合并为UC1
end note

note right of UC4
  **用例合并理由**
  BR-EQP-003/004/007/008/010/012均围绕
  “归还验收”这一核心业务活动，合并为UC4
end note

note right of UC8
  **用例拆分理由**
  合同变更（BR-ORD-001/003/005）与标准租赁流程
  （BR-ORD-002）业务流程不同，拆分为独立用例
end note

@enduml
```
@enduml